Interface InteractionId

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Hl7v2InteractionId<T>, Hl7v3InteractionId<ConfigType>, WsInteractionId<ConfigType>, XdsInteractionId<ConfigType>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ATNA.Interactions, ATNA.Interactions, CONTINUA_HRN.Interactions, CustomFhirComponent, MHD.QueryInteractions, MHD.QueryInteractions, MHD.RetrieveInteractions, MHD.RetrieveInteractions, MHD.SubmitInteractions, MHD.SubmitInteractions, PAM.Interactions, PDQ.Interactions, PDQM.Interactions, PDQM.Interactions, PDQV3.Interactions, PIX.FeedInteractions, PIX.QueryInteractions, PIXM.Interactions, PIXM.Interactions, PIXV3.Interactions, QED.Interactions, RAD.Interactions, SerializableEnumInteractionId, XCA.Interactions, XCDR.Interactions, XCF.Interactions, XCMU.Interactions, XCPD.Interactions, XDM.Interactions, XDR.Interactions, XDS.Interactions, XPID.Interactions

    public interface InteractionId
    eHealth interaction ID. Implementations of this interface should ensure that instances are singletons. The recommended way to achieve this is using enums.

    Dmytro Rud
